<span class="name"><a name="94464"></a></span><span class="postdetails">#1:&nbsp;<font color=black><b>Everquest, Athlon64 and Cool&amp;Quiet problem</b> Author:&nbsp;<b>Silamael</b>,&nbsp;</font></span><span class="postdetails"><font color=black></font></span>
<a href="viewtopic.php?p=94464#94464"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Posted: Mon Jan 24, 2005 5:53 am</font><span class="gen"><br>
